resource/History_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's French charm, you know, beheaded people, red wine, and blood all over the place - it's romantic, it's normal.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.8086531946956889, \"rank\": 0.2366224402087925, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"red wine\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is nothing satanic,\\\" he added with a laugh.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"a laugh\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The musician continued: \\\"Franceis a country that made a separation between the state and religion during the revolution.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The musician\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"a separation\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"the state\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"the revolution\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's something very important, very dear to the foundation of republican France.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republicanism\", \"score\": 0.9999495665050485, \"rank\": 3.0836151656579826e-05, \"text\": \"republican\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbped